=== _call_impl 入口的 compile-aware 分支 ===
  L1:     def _call_impl(self, *args, **kwargs):
  L2:         forward_call = (self._slow_forward if torch._C._get_tracing_state() else self.forward)
  L3:         # If we don't have any hooks, we want to skip the rest of the logic in
